biolockj.node

Interface OtuNode

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Kraken2Node, KrakenNode, MetaphlanNode, OtuNodeImpl, QiimeNode, RdpNode, SlimmNode

    public interface OtuNode
    Classes that implement this interface store taxonomy assignment info for one sequence, as output by a classifier. ParserModules read ClassifierModule output to build standardized OTU abundance tables. Each line of classifier output is parsed for the OTU name, OTU count, and sample ID. Note that if data is demultiplexed, the Sample ID is extracted from the file name instead of the sequence header.
